    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Idle到Loading的触发条件是\"Load Program\"对吧？那Loading之后呢，直接就能运行吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Load Program"
