      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以Validating有两个分支：到Ready是\"Program Valid\"，到Error是\"Invalid Program\"。那Error之后能恢复吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Validating",
        "Ready",
        "Error",
        "Program Valid",
        "Invalid Program"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以，Error状态要支持Clear Error操作，清除后回到Idle。另外Ready之后用户Start Program进入Running，这是核心运行态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
