        "Start Program"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Running状态我加上了。考虑到实际业务，运行中可能需要暂停和换料，是不是要设计Paused和Dressing两个子状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
